{"tid":1297833,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)怪奇物語","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T22:56:26.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b550852078f8ae52f09785f4f478a9a988190c2","tid":1297833,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=76f5a001\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e0caed98\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=8df1f605\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.horace.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/strangerthingsposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.horace.org%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fstrangerthingsposter.jpg&h=a330edad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mrbuzz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/stranger-things-2-e1509278997672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrbuzz.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fstranger-things-2-e1509278997672.jpg&h=82e7d808&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://vmus.online/img/2019/07/p2558683543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmus.online%2Fimg%2F2019%2F07%2Fp2558683543.jpg&h=49316fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主角將會聚焦在由米莉芭比布朗Millie Bobby Brown飾演的「11號」身上，故事從第二季之後一年的1985年Hawkins 小鎮發展，在炎熱的夏季中小朋友們也開始放暑假了，今年暑假小鎮最重要的大事就是一個新的購物中心正式開幕，而這群霍金斯的主角們也開始邁入轉大人的青春期，浪漫情愫也跟隨隱藏危機的詭異氛圍蔓延茁壯。前所未見的威脅和原來舊有的黑暗力量一起出現。伊萊雯和他的朋友們都知道邪惡的力量不會被終結，而且牠還開始進化。他們為了生存必須團結起來，因為友誼才能戰勝恐懼<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=9324ed0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=251d97b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee9dac4320dcd316b50e1d7019915df2fabefe7","tid":1297833,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0685cdc9dc564dbc0d91b0c755344dbe37c4cd9f","tid":1297833,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019